name: ⭕️ MLNDR Founders Collection: 006/Tango
description: Meet Tango, an advanced protection dog armed with more than a set of teeth. Thanks to a massive 10,000% cognitive boost, Tango was recognized as a fully self-aware being thus receiving Olodziar’s citizenship and joining the thousands of dogs who are now part of the country’s workforce. He currently works as a security guard at The Maze, a local Neural-Quantum® nightclub that serves legal (and illegal) synthetics. After his day is over, he comes back to the MLNDR’s place, where he cuddles with Greg every night and protects them from any possible harm by activating his deep-dream surveillance mode.
